dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Carl Brown. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Carl. My name is Margaret Mitchell.
Nice to meet you, Margaret. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's five six two three eight.
Thank you, Margaret. And for verification purposes, could you tell me the street number of the address listed on your policy?
Thank you for confirming the information, Margaret. How can I assist you today with Old Stone Auto Insurance?
I'd like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Margaret. I can help you with that. Let's get started with the details.
Thank you for your time, Margaret. If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
